# Define UV cell

}

Regression of signature vs age, by cell type

my_sigs = unique(sig_prop_type2_Nmelt$variable)
pvalue = R2 = beta = pvalue_no4 = R2_no4 = beta_no4 = vector()
for (i in 1:length(my_sigs)){
  mylm = summary(lm(value~Age, data = subset(sig_prop_type2_Nmelt, variable==my_sigs[i]) ) )
 pvalue[i] = mylm$coefficients[2,4]
 beta[i] = mylm$coefficients[2,1]
 R2[i] = mylm$r.squared
 mylm_no4 = summary(lm(value~Age, data = subset(sig_prop_type2_Nmelt, variable==my_sigs[i] & Age!= 4) ) )
 pvalue_no4[i] = mylm_no4$coefficients[2,4]
 beta_no4[i] = mylm_no4$coefficients[2,1]
 R2_no4[i] = mylm_no4$r.squared
}
age_sig_lm = data.frame(my_sigs , pvalue, beta, R2, pvalue_no4, beta_no4,R2_no4)
